386→                        <div id="content">Is every sufficiently large integer of the form\[ap^2+b\]for some prime $p$ and integer $a\geq 1$ and $0\leq b&#60;p$?</div>
387→                        <div id="problem_id"><a href="/676">#676</a>: <a href="#cite-Er79-676" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er79','676'); return false;">[Er79]</a><a href="#cite-Er79d-676" onclick="event.preventDefault();addNewBox('Er79d','676'); return false;">[Er79d]</a></div>
